snippet.title: inZOI 2023 Official Gameplay Demo
snippet.description:
Please check out the in-game footage of inZOI, a life simulation game where players become gods within the game, allowing them to change everything as they wish and experience endless new stories in various forms of life.
(※This video is from the development stage.)

00:38 Characters & Life
02:34 Character Creation
03:38 Build Mode
04:54 Director’s Mode - Schedule, Weather, City
05:17 Filter
05:26 Relationships
